{"tid":1865422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街！香港2月8前玩撚完","createTime":"2020-02-06T07:31:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T08:48:46.000Z","uid":102384,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0d156dd9fa2b6e321f453213e46db4e1a47d4777","tid":1865422,"uid":102384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T07:31:24.000Z","msg":"我有個朋友呀媽係做保險而且藍到裂開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢本人就係做內地客群為主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁今日我朋友就同我講<br />\n佢呀媽表示依幾日上面會有好多人趕被隔離前衝落黎香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為香港醫療系統比較好而且內地既醫療負荷接近爆煲<br />\n所以就黎香港有更好既醫療服務<br />\n佢仲話今日先有個發緊燒既<br />\n食左退燒藥衝鳩左落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果朋友老母係認真嘅都幾撚恐怖<br />\n<br />\n但邊有人咁撚白癡同人講我之後幾日會隔離班播毒者架！係就安排好即日講完即日做啦屌佢老未！啲人咪趁早擁鳩晒落黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關又唔閪封仲要整埋d垃圾安排！<br />\n好想香港有個類似特朗普既特首<br />\n俾我地為香港努力既香港人擁有香港人優先<br />\n唉好撚灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a42135a200f0c11a303c7ec16df69e1dde88eda","tid":1865422,"uid":124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci